===登地聯===
就在迪華里斯被李斯特城放棄同日，他轉投了[[登地聯足球會|登地聯]]重遇惜日的領隊奇治·尼雲<ref name="Levein is re-united with de Vries">{{cite news| title = Levein is re-united with de Vries| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/7205468.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2008-01-25| accessdate = 2009-01-03| archive-date = 2008-01-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080127163519/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/7205468.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。他在蘇格蘭聯賽盃決賽對[[流浪者足球俱樂部|格拉斯哥流浪]]的賽事中攻入其轉投的首球，聯賽入球則在六天後對[[馬瑟韋爾足球會|馬瑟韋爾]]的賽事中攻入。迪華里斯在2008年6月約滿後，被[[金堡爾|金堡爾]]邀請前往試腳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cambuur.nl/cambuur/news/article235238.ece|title=Notable debutant at SC Cambuur: Mark de Vries|date=2008-07-29|publisher=SC Cambuur|language=nl|accessdate=2008-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080928050238/http://www.cambuur.nl/cambuur/news/article235238.ece|archivedate=2008-09-28}}</ref>。

===金堡爾===
2008年8月28日，迪華里斯加盟金堡爾。他在處子戰對[[艾文足球會|艾文]]的賽事中攻入1球，協助球隊以6-2大勝對手。

